# IMPORTANT: Never commit secrets. Use dotnet user-secrets or environment vars.
# appsettings.json        — committed with placeholder values only (safe to track).
# appsettings.Production.json — committed; contains NO secrets. All Supabase
#                               credentials are set as Azure App Service environment
#                               variables (Supabase__Url, Supabase__ServiceRoleKey, etc.).
# appsettings.Development.json — committed; contains only log-level overrides.

# ── Supabase CLI ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.supabase/

